                "description": "Our friends at Denver Health started running messaging campaigns through Epic just over a year ago to help ensure that parents got their kids in for annual wellchild visits.\n\nTheir outreach efforts began to soar when COVID-19 vaccinations became available, and they’ve since started campaigns to help patients monitor their A1C, manage their hypertension, and get early screenings for colorectal cancer.\n\nNow, they have their eyes set on even more—like how campaigns can improve providers’ understanding of social drivers of health, and how campaigns can give patients and docs more face-to-face time during appointments.\n\nRachel Everhart, Denver Health’s director of research, and Sam Seering, our Cheers product manager, sat down to discuss all of this and more.\n\nCheck it out: https://lnkd.in/ga63BK4y\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #innovation",
