                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7009520098575097856",
                "followers": 515027,
                "date": "1mo",
                "description": "If you’re keeping track at home, holistic care just took yet another step forward.\n\nOur friends at MemorialCare and Pacific Dental Services are bringing opening facilities where their doctors and dentists can come together under a single roof, creating one-stop shops for whole person care.\n\nConnected by Epic, the providers at these facilities will be able to inform their care for patients using the same comprehensive health record.\n\nFrom Judy: “Healthcare outcomes are vastly improved when providers have quick access to all relevant information on a patient. Our partnership with Pacific Dental Services that achieved final implementation to their 900+ dental practices earlier this year was a significant step forward in linking dental and medical professionals. We’re proud to be a part of extending that link to now include merging our software with dental and medical professionals under one roof.” \n\nCongrats, folks!\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/ewCcS5V4\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #innovation",
