                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7009224011557593089",
                "followers": 515027,
                "date": "1mo",
                "description": "Our friends at CVS Health hosted a live Q&A this morning and there was an Epic mention! Check out David’s interview below.\n \nHere’s a snippet: “The electronic health record is basically the backbone across all of our clinical systems. So, whether you're in MinuteClinic or Coram or even in pharmacy now, we're using Epic to be able to coordinate care and make sure that we use data to help improve the care of patients no matter where you show up within the CVS health system.”",
                "reactions_count": 118,
