                "date": "2w",
                "description": "Making life-saving diagnostic tests available to more patients can come down to scalability—how easy it is for health systems to connect to external diagnostic labs, send orders to those labs, and receive results in a timely fashion.\n\nWhen providers connect with a specialty diagnostic lab through Aura, they can send orders and receive results through their usual Epic workflows, leaving point-to-point interfaces and fax machines (yes, they still exist) in the dust.\n\nHere’s just one example: After connecting with Exact Sciences through Aura, Epic’s Orders and Results Anywhere framework, Ochsner Health screened nearly 5,000 patients for colorectal cancer. 77% of those patients—more than 3,700 people—had never been screened for colorectal cancer before.\n\nMembers of the Epic community can check out the Ochsner-Exact UGM 2021 presentation for more: https://lnkd.in/etzguzKU\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #innovation",
