                "description": "We never shared our 2022 Spotify Wrapped with you, but we do want to share something a little different: our Year in Review.\n\nEvery year, we come together to celebrate the numbers behind what our community has achieved using Epic. Here’s a look at a distilled version 😊\n\nPS – if you have thoughts on what would appear on our 2022 Wrapped, let us know in the comments!\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #innovation",
