                "followers": 533396,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "For many health systems, finding the right clinical trials for their patients can be time-consuming and challenging, making it hard to provide potentially life-saving treatments to those in need. To make it easier to connect with the right opportunities, health systems in the Epic community can participate in Clinical Trial Matchmaking (CTM).\n\nUsing Cosmos, the CTM program connects health systems with sponsored research opportunities suited to the patients they treat. This increases the number of clinical trials that a health system can consider while minimizing the time they spend evaluating each one. Ultimately, the goal is clinical trials that are 1) more efficient, 2) more diverse, and as a result, 3) more effective for patients. \n\nIf you represent a provider organization interested in CTM, send us an email at LifeSciences@epic.com\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #research",
