                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7034519432924188672",
                "followers": 533396,
                "date": "3w",
                "description": "To make telehealth a more convenient experience for patients, provider organizations that use Epic can offer 24/7, 50-state virtual urgent care coverage through our Telehealth Anywhere platform.\n\nDuring surges in demand or after hours, provider organizations can use Telehealth Anywhere to connect patients to their preferred telehealth partners. Rather than routing patients through disconnected, standalone systems, those partners can provide cohesive care experiences—and maintain consistent documentation—directly in Epic. \n\nLearn more about the first Telehealth Anywhere connection between Spectrum Health and KeyCare: https://lnkd.in/dx6fDiPK\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #telehealth",
