                "followers": 546103,
                "date": "6d",
                "description": "Our friends at The Royal Children's Hospital recently equipped all clinical staff with smartphones connected to Epic, replacing several older devices in use (goodbye, pagers!) with a common platform.\n\nThe change helped Royal Children’s improve nurse satisfaction by 9% and saves an average of 26 minutes per nurse, per shift.\n\nCongrats, folks!\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/g3PUfpd9\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #nursing",
