                "followers": 546103,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "Our friends at Mount Sinai Health System are collaborating with The New York Public Library on a cool project called Take Charge with MyChart.\n\nThe idea is simple: go to a focal, inclusive point of the community—the library—so that you can get people from a wide variety of backgrounds acquainted with MyChart. With free classes that cover online scheduling, reviewing labs and medical history, attending virtual visits, and more, Mount Sinai aims to address the “digital divide” that can impact health equity.\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/ggHUtJhk\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #community",
