                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7044284085720006656",
                "followers": 546103,
                "date": "1mo",
                "description": "Our friends at Manchester University NHS Foundation Trust, the largest trust in the UK, recently shared a few accomplishments since their Epic go-live last September, including:\n\n· Avoiding 36 critical medication administration errors in the last 6 months\n\n· Saving £500,000 on printing consumables and £300,000 through reduced use of legacy systems\n\n· Reducing turnaround time on outpatient letters by seven days\n\nThese accomplishments are years in the making. Congrats, folks, on all of the excellent work so far!\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/gXeBE4XA\n\n#healthcare #healthIT #innovation",
