                "date": "1d",
                "description": "“I have been intentional about my life choices, and with each conscious and intentional step, I’ve become stronger as a person and as a leader.” \n\nIn this inspiring TEDx Talk, Cardinal Health CIO Michelle D Greene, shares four pillars that guide her to live and lead intentionally, and her passion to continuously develop herself and others on her journey as a #technology #leader. \nhttp://spr.ly/60483BiDo",
