                "description": "Our CIO Michelle D Greene is paving the way in the tech industry as the only female to make the list of notable CIO appointments by CIO Dive: Information and Enterprise Technology News. \n\nHer authentic leadership is transforming our technology organization to drive meaningful change across the healthcare continuum. http://spr.ly/6043MhGVH #leadership #tech #healthcare",
