                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7003700758210629632",
                "followers": 516400,
                "date": "6d",
                "description": "Cardinal Health's culture of continuous learning enables our team to explore new technologies that foster innovation to improve experiences for our customers. \n\nOur work with cloud technology landed us a Google Cloud Healthcare and Life Sciences Award, which highlights the very best examples of customer and partner innovation.\n\nOur congratulations go out to the Cardinal Health Cloud teams, who earned the award and continue to create tangible digital solutions that will impact health care in the future. #cloud #healthcare Todd Fisher",
