                "followers": 32002,
                "date": "46m",
                "description": "The gifting tree is back for a second year at Designer Outlet Neumünster. Guests of our centre are invited to give children who are going to be in hospital this Christmas a treat and make a wish come true.\n\nThe centre’s gifting tree has been decorated with white stars, each marked with a toy in the price range of €5 to €150. Each star can be chosen, and the value of the gift is donated in Guest Services. Taking on the role of Santa’s elves, the centre staff will then purchase the present on the guest’s behalf.  \n\nSo far, the centre has collected over €3000 and still has three weeks left to collect more wishes. All gifts will then be donated to the children’s ward at Friedrich Ebert Hospital in Neumünster, providing Christmas magic to those who deserve it most. \n\nLast year, the centre collected more than 150 gifts worth €2,650. On top of the gifts, the Centre donated €20,000 to the hospital which was used for children's psychological support and two paediatric lung machines. \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Neumünster #GiftingTree #Christmas",
