                "date": "1d",
                "description": "Designer Outlet Paris-Giverny has held the first day of its two-day job fair, recruiting employees to join the centre and its brand partner teams ahead of the grand opening early next year.\n\nIn an interview with France 3 Normandie, General Manager Myriem Nieres-Tavernier spoke about the importance of the large-scale recruitment event and what it means for the region.\n\n“We are delighted to be able to welcome so many people from the region and the surrounding areas to the centre,” she said. “We are aware that it is a difficult time for recruiters and candidates. It has always been a top priority for us to work with the local authorities and our employment partners to prepare for events just like this.”\n\nYou can find the full clip in French from 3:04 - 4:00 at the link below.\n\n#McArthurGlen #MyMcarthurglen #CareersFair #Paris #Giverny #DesignerOutlet #BePartOfSomethingExtraordinary #Normandie",
