                "description": "Last month, Designer Outlet Swindon invited local influencers to discuss all things fashion at their Autumn/Winter 22 event. \n\nSwindon invited fashion writer and Director-at-Large at Glamour UK, Alexandra Fullerton, who hosted a deep dive into the season’s latest trends. In keeping with our Recycle Your Fashion programme, the influencers were also treated to an exclusive capsule wardrobe styling session. \n\nLocal businesses were invited to help run the evening and we welcomed event stylist It's Your Parties, florist Wild Though Floristry, caterer Little Grazey, and event photographer Hello Loveli. \n\n \n#McArthurGlen #Swindon #DesignerOutlet #AW22 #TrendTalk #FashionCommunity",
