                "description": "We are delighted to partner with Premier League football club ESTAC Troyes to show our pride for the local Aube region of Designer Outlet Troyes. \n\nJoining for the launch of the new Trends Full Black campaign are Troyes players Rony Lopes, Adil Rami, Wilson Odobert, Gauthier Gallon and Thierno Baldé\n\nTo celebrate the new season, our Troyes centre will offer a programme of exceptional activities and events to guests coming from the region and throughout France. \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Troyes #ESTAC #Football #SportCommunity #AubeRegion",
