                "date": "1w",
                "description": "For the first time in two years, Designer Outlet Roosendaal kicked off the festive period in spectacular fashion with the return of their Lights On event. \n\nOur guests were invited to an evening of festive entertainment including dancing reindeer, trapeze artists, and circus performers. Underneath the Christmas tree, a gospel choir performed carols, creating a merry soundtrack for the evening before the night ended with a colourful fireworks display. Plus, there were plenty of areas for guests to take festive family photos. \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Roosendaal #LightsOn #FestiveSeason #Christmas",
