                "followers": 32002,
                "date": "1w",
                "description": "Shopping Week was back at Designer Outlet Parndorf earlier this month with tempting discounts off the outlet price. With opening hours of 09:00-21:00 on weekdays and 09:00-18:00 on Saturday, the extra-long opening hours and additional discounts were not the only reason to visit. \n\nDuring the week, Parndorf planned a special event programme so our guests left with treasured memories. Joining us were entertainers including LED Diamonds, a live DJ and other surprises around the centre.  \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Parndorf",
