                "date": "1w",
                "description": "Designer Outlet Málaga was thrilled to welcome CH Carolina Herrera to its offering of luxury brands this month. This is the first ever store for the label in McArthurGlen’s portfolio. \n\nJavier Mendizabal, Malaga’s Centre Manager, said: “We're delighted to welcome CH Carolina Herrera to the centre’s brand mix. Along with our existing brands like Prada, Moncler, Zegna, Escada and many more, the new addition will help to cement Designer Outlet Málaga as the premium shopping destination in the Costa del Sol.” \n\nOffering ready-to-wear and accessories collections for men, women and children, the brand is set to appeal to domestic and international customers alike. \n\n#McArthurGlen #Malaga #Leasing #DesignerOutlet",
