                "followers": 32002,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "Designer Outlet Roubaix proudly welcomed the opening of a high-end gym club, the first in our portfolio. \n\nFitness Park allows guests to focus on their physical wellbeing across different sports facilities including bodybuilding, cross-training, cycling, fight park and cardio-training. There’s also a women’s only area and all guests can enjoy a moment of relaxation after a good workout with the view on the terrace overlooking the centre. \n\nWe are delighted to welcome a new concept to our centre! \n\n#FitnessPark #DesignerOutlet #Roubaix #Sport #Community",
