                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7015987955483713536",
                "followers": 32282,
                "date": "3d",
                "description": "Our sincerest thanks to guests of Designer Outlet Ochtrup, who last year donated over €11,000 at the centre’s Cistern of Wishes. \n\nDiscovered during renovation works, the cistern, which was once part of a textile dye factory, now serves as a place where guests to the centre can take a moment to reflect, make a wish and share a gesture of goodwill. \n\nThe donation was gifted across 15 charities local to the centre, including the local Rotary Club who organised aid for Ukraine. With last year’s gift, the Cistern of Wishes has collected over €100,000 since 2015. \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutletOtchrup #Charity",
