                "followers": 32282,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "On behalf of everyone at McArthurGlen Group, we are sending warm festive wishes to our valued guests, colleagues, brand partners and suppliers. Thank you all for your continued support throughout 2022!  \n \nHappy Holidays! \nFelices Fiestas! \nJoyeuses Fêtes! \nBuone Feste! \nFrohe Feiertage! \nFijne feestdagen! \nκαλές διακοπες! \n \n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlets #HappyHolidays",
