                "company_id": 5224619,
                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7011637316238639104",
                "followers": 32282,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "Guests to Designer Outlet Parndorf can arrive at the centre car-free, using a new state-of-the-art electric-powered bus service.\n\nRunning every 30 minutes from the local train station, the electric-powered service will improve accessibility to the centre. With a low-floor ramp for prams and wheelchair users, the service ensures that shoppers of all abilities can visit the centre with ease. \n\nMario Schwann, General Manager, said: \"We are very happy that with the public bus connection of the Designer Outlet Parndorf a long-pursued heart project is being implemented. For our customers from Austria and the surrounding neighbouring countries, this will make it even easier to reach the largest designer outlet in Central Europe conveniently, cheaply and environmentally friendly. For the more than 1,900 employees at the McArthurGlen Designer Outlet, the public connection is a welcome support\". \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Pandorf",
