                "company_id": 5224619,
                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7011367316898684929",
                "followers": 32282,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "Two new brands have opened at Designer Outlet Roermond this month, boosting shopping opportunities on offer at our centre. \n\nIRO PARIS was born in Paris and takes its inspiration from 70’s and 80’s American Rock scene and the desire to build a simple and strong wardrobe.  \n\nAlso attracting guests to the centre is Isabel Marant. The eponymous label was founded in 1995 and is known for its Parisien and laid-back aesthetic.  \n\nDesigner Outlet Roermond is the second McArthurGlen location for both brands and we’re delighted they are expanding their footprint within our portfolio. \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Roermond #IRO #IsabelMarant",
