                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7011278252639928322",
                "followers": 32282,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "The largest outdoor real ice rink in the North of England returns to Designer Outlet York as the centre hosts Yorkshire’s Winter Wonderland for its 12th season. \n\nAfter taking a spin around the ice, guests can warm up with some festive treats in the cosy après-skate café. Or if they fancy something different, visitors can relive the golden era of fairgrounds at the vintage funfair which comes complete with a 1936 Speedway, 1930s Chair-o-Plane and rare Brooklands Dodgems.  \n\nPaul Tyler, Centre Manager at York, said: “We love hosting Yorkshire’s Winter Wonderland … we are in our 12th year now and this important event always helps bring Christmas alive at the Centre. Our guests simply love it.” \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #York #WinterWonderland",
