                "description": "Designer Outlet Serravalle welcomes two new restaurants to the centre. \n\nOur guests can now sample some of America’s favourite treats from California Bakery including Maine lobster rolls, Californian burgers and NY bagels. After opening in Milan more than 20 years ago, the chain now has over twenty restaurants across northern Italy. \n\nWe are also proud to welcome God Save the Food to the centre, as they open their fifth venue in Italy. The restaurant serves tasty dishes in a stylish and sleek setting. \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Serravalle #CaliforniaBakery #GodSaveTheFood",
