                "description": "Designer Outlet West Midlands kicked off the festive season in style with a spectacular influencer Christmas event.  \n \nOrganised in collaboration with our brand partner PizzaExpress Express, our centre hosted 16 influencers for a celebratory meal and drinks, followed by a Christmas workshop hosted by calligraphy professionals, Mellor & Rose. The influencers created their own Christmas gift tags and bespoke greeting cards. \n \n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlets #WestMidlands",
