                "description": "Designer Outlet Serravalle creates an unforgettable, immersive experience with Santa’s magical kitchen. \n\nHidden in the base of the 32-metre tall Christmas tree, shoppers will be transported to a festive wonderland as they step into a cosy kitchen where children can help the elves to create a festive feast and meet Santa. \n\nLED screens look onto a snowy scene whilst the scent of a freshly baked apple pie fills the air, creating a multi-sensory experience which is sure to get guests into the festive spirit. \n\n#DesignerOutletSerravalle #Christmas #SantasKitchen",
