                "description": "We are proud to welcome back prison community project, Fuga di Sapori to McArthurGlen Designer Outlet Serravalle. \n\nFuga di Sapori enables inmates to learn a new skill such as carpentry or sustainable agriculture and the skillfully made produce is available to purchase at a pop-up store in our centre. All proceeds support job placements and the purchase of new tools. \n\nOur people in Serravalle were inspired by the collaboration and spent time volunteering to assist the store. Community is one of our most important values at McArthurGlen and we are dedicated to supporting our local areas at any opportunity.  \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #Serravalle #FugadiSapori #Volunteering",
