                "description": "To celebrate a spectacular collaboration, McArthurGlen Designer Outlet La Reggia was transformed into an immersive, life-size version of a Monopoly board, to reveal a special edition game.\n\nInspired by the game’s ability to bring family and friends together through play, guests were invited to win a copy of the game to take home.  \n\nThis is the first-ever edition of the classic board game that is based on a shopping destination. \n\nFabio Rinaldi, Centre Manager, said: \"This special edition of Monopoly allows us to bring a bit of La Reggia into the homes and carefree moments of our customers. In a hyper-digitized era, Monopoly is a return to play, to socializing, to being together with friends and family, around a table. Precisely for this reason, we have decided that the game will not be for sale, but our gift.\" \n\n#McArthurGlen #DesignerOutlet #LaReggia #MonopolyGame #boardgame #MakingTheExtraordinaryPossible",
