                "date": "11h",
                "description": "Our 2022 Citizenship Report shares the progress made, actions taken, and impact created by our people and for the planet through Community Impact, Equality & Inclusion, Environmental Sustainability, and Ethics & Responsibility.\n \nFrom serving people with superior solutions that are sustainable, to using our global reach to create meaningful impact, we’ve built Citizenship into how we do business every day.\n \nLearn how we’re committed to being a Force For Growth and a Force For Good; read our 2022 Citizenship Report: https://lnkd.in/e2rntPDt",
