                "followers": 7202755,
                "date": "2d",
                "description": "The #PGInnovation in Dawn Powerwash Dish Spray saves time and water, \"elevating the everyday.\"\n\nWith grease-cutting technology and a powerful spray nozzle, the spray-activated suds eliminate the need for soaking by clinging to food soils, cleaning grease 5x than our Dawn Non-Concentrated product. Dawn Powerwash cuts the amount of water needed to hand wash dishes in half compared to the water used when running the tap continually to hand wash dishes. \n\nNo wonder Dawn made Fast Company's 2022 Brands that Matter list for Elevating the Everyday! \n\nRead all about the #sustainable #innovation in Dawn Powerwash Dish Spray from Fast Company: https://lnkd.in/eFZV4Bm #CES #BrandsThatMatter",
