                "followers": 7229040,
                "date": "5d",
                "description": "Laundry day just got easier thanks to a new product created by P&G innovator, Jack.  \n \nJack English says sometimes you need something a little extra to boost your regular laundry routine, so he and his team helped launch Downy Rinse & Refresh – a product that enables people to get better odor removal and cleaner laundry! \n\n“The issue with rinsing is that everybody knows they have to do it, but they don't think of it as a way to make progress today. And what we found is that by having products that are specifically designed for the rinse, we can create whole new mechanisms that allow people to get better performance than was ever possible with a detergent alone,” said English, who has been with P&G for 25 years. \n\nOh, and if you happen to forget your laundry in the washer after it runs, Downy Rinse & Refresh will smell good even up to 24 hours later! \n\nDowny Rinse & Refresh goes in the softener dispenser of your washer and will dispense when your laundry is in the rinse stage of the cycle. \n \nTo learn more about English’s story: https://lnkd.in/e9brv5GB #PGInnovation",
