                "description": "Almost 1/3 of the global population now lives in water-stressed regions, and 2/3 is projected to live in water-stressed regions by 2025.\n\nAs 2022 comes to a close, we can’t help but reflect on how important water is in our daily lives, which is why we are working to help build a #WaterPositiveFuture. By restoring water for people and nature in water-stressed areas around the world, reducing water in our operations, and responding to water challenges through innovation and partnerships, we hope to help address the global water crisis. \n\nLearn about the steps that we are taking and how you can help in the new year: http://spr.ly/60463MFyi",
