                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7020792527624560641",
                "followers": 7254728,
                "date": "1h",
                "description": "“I’m a legacy, I’m a legacy, I know. I am his dream, I am his dream.” - performer Destiny L \n\nToday, leaders from P&G celebrated the life and legacy of Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr., reflecting on how moments can evolve into movements.\n \nThe 2023 King Legacy Celebration at the National Underground Railroad Freedom Center  was an inspiring morning of music, dance and reflection. \n\nLearn more about P&G’s commitment to Equality & Inclusion: https://lnkd.in/eMQ5_3R",
