                "date": "4d",
                "description": "Today we announced that Mielle Organics LLC®, the popular hair care brand rooted in natural ingredients and focused on serving the needs of Black women, will join PG Beauty, pending regulatory approval, further expanding access to healthy hair products and services for textured hair consumers around the world.\n\nThis move will mean further expanding access to healthy hair products and services for textured hair consumers around the world. Mielle will operate as an independent subsidiary of P&G Beauty, continuing to be led by co-founders Monique and Melvin Rodriguez as CEO and COO, respectively.\n\nIn service of our shared values, Mielle and P&G have each committed $10 million to Mielle Cares, a non-profit aimed at providing resources and support to advance education and economic opportunities in Black and Brown communities. For P&G, this investment further expands our commitment to advance gender and racial equity through award-winning platforms like My Black is Beautiful and Widen the Screen and reinforces our Responsible Beauty pledge to be a force for growth, a force for good, and a force for Beauty in the world. Welcome to the family!\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/eMGtYySY",
