                "description": "Dishwashing is the second most hated household chore in the U.S., according to P&G dish scientists.\n \nThat’s why our team is dedicated to making the task as easy as possible. Cheddar News Senior Reporter Michelle Castillo toured P&G’s Dish Lab to report on one of our latest innovations: Cascade Platinum Plus. #PGInnovation\n \n“To alleviate the stress of scrubbing, P&G invented Cascade Platinum Plus. The new pod is claimed to allow people to scrape, load, run the dishwasher and get clean plates – all without prewashing or soaking,” writes Castillo.\n \nFor the full story: https://lnkd.in/gJSEU5Gf",
