                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7027347129803137024",
                "followers": 7295233,
                "date": "2d",
                "description": "We aspire to build a world free from gender bias — with equal voice, equal opportunity, and equal representation for all individuals. \n\nThis longtime aspiration is shared by not only our P&G people but also our brands. Most recently, Dawn & Swiffer partnered with Hello Sunshine 's  Fair Play Life to launch the educational initiative Home Eq[uity], which is designed to #CloseTheChoreGap by teaching the next generation how to distribute household work fairly across all family members.\n\nP&G’s inclusion in the 2023 Bloomberg Gender Equality Index reflects a shared commitment to embed #equality and #inclusion into our business as we serve consumers every day. By investing in our employees and supporting our leading partners and changemakers around the globe, we are working to tackle bias, inspire dialogue and understanding, and take action to create a workplace and a world where everyone sees equal. \n\nLearn more: https://lnkd.in/er-YkJT #WeSeeEqual #BloombergGE",
