                "description": "Our brands, partners and P&G Studios, including the signature program the Queen Collective, develop and produce stories that help shine a light on under-represented voices and untold stories.\n \nAt this year’s #SundanceFilmFestival, our goal was to help create spaces for representative and equitable storytelling – from an intimate panel with our Queen Collective filmmakers to the screening of the feature-length documentary #FairPlay, in partnership with Hello Sunshine, to having a discussion about the importance and significance of names in the AAPI community for inclusion.\n \nTo learn more about the films, partnerships and initiatives that we helped spotlight at this year’s festival, visit: https://lnkd.in/ewD-Gbsz",
