                "description": "Delivering new digital experiences is key to providing superior quality products and fostering a stronger connection between brands and consumers. \n\nAs early adopters of 2D barcodes, P&G is already leveraging this technology on Gillette to create even better consumer experiences through product education. But there are so many additional opportunities through application of this digital transformation to even more products. It opens the door for improved product accessibility, sustainability efforts and efficiency across operations.   \n\nTo learn how we’re embracing this innovation, watch P&G Senior Vice President, Information Technology, Alfredo Colas' discussion with GS1 at #GS1GlobalForum2023: https://lnkd.in/ea5AQVRc\n#PGInnovation",
