                "reshared_post_description": "It’s finally time for Downy Unstopables’ big reveal! For 12 weeks, Downy has been gearing up for the Super Bowl by enlisting a celebrity skeptic to put the 12-week freshness claim to the test before agreeing to appear in our campaign. We are excited to say he is a believer and Danny McBride is now Downy McBride. It’s been a great journey seeing people and media engaging with us for months and we are thrilled to be part of the big game to bring the amazing smell of Downy Unstopables to the masses. Time for us all to #sniffittobelieveit, #DownyMcBride",
