                "followers": 7310243,
                "date": "3d",
                "description": "On International Day of Women and Girls in Science, we are committed to supporting the careers and courageous leadership of women and girls in #STEM. \n\nAs a company built on superior innovation in our products for consumers over 185 years, we value the important contributions women in science make, not only to P&G’s success, but to our world’s.    \n\nYet, today women make up only 28% of the workforce in STEM, and men vastly outnumber women majoring in most STEM fields in higher education.  \n\nThat’s why today – and every day - we celebrate emerging women leaders in STEM and we will continue taking action to advance gender equality in STEM. \n\nLearn more about how we are supporting and inspiring the leaders of tomorrow: https://lnkd.in/ea87R6hn\n\n#WeSeeEqual #FaceTheSTEMGap #WomeninScience",
