                "date": "4d",
                "description": "Accessibility is a driving factor in how we create safe, sustainable and inclusively designed packaging.\n \nPAC Global recognized our team behind the Ariel ECOCLIC® box - the first Ariel laundry pack to be both certified child-safe and designed to be inclusive and intuitive to use for all adults including those with dexterity, visual and/or cognitive impairments.\n \nLearn more on the P&G Blog: https://lnkd.in/ghvdAGSu #DisabilityConfident #DisabilityInclusion",
