                "date": "5d",
                "description": "Innovator Ryan Butler started as an intern at P&G in 2013. Ten years later he is the Brand Director for Secret North America. \n \nRyan currently leads Secret Deodorant, delivering superior sweat and odor protection in products like the Weightless Dry Spray Antiperspirant Deodorant and communicating product superiority. \n \nRyan’s passion for his job, comes from the people he works with and the impact he makes.  \n \n“I love many things about my job,” Ryan says, “but the part that I’m most passionate about is coaching and mentoring people. I love to see people grow and lead bigger projects with confidence.” \n \nHe counts his biggest accomplishment as his work on P&G’s film The Look. “The film follows a Black man throughout his typical day to show what he encounters on an all too regular basis,” Ryan says.\n \nCheck out Ryan and our other #BlackHistoryMonth #PGInnovation talent on our latest blog: https://lnkd.in/emhmUpPc",
