                "followers": 7343669,
                "date": "2d",
                "description": "Today we celebrate our longstanding partnership with the World Wildlife Fund (WWF) and the positive impact we have had on wildlife conservation together.\n\nIn a new blog post from WWF, P&G’s Nature and Biodiversity leader and WWF Rising Star Ashley Kuhn speaks about our collaboration to protect Malayan tigers and landscapes in the Central Forest Spine of Peninsular Malaysia that takes place on four Forest Linkages and two around Cameron Highlands.\n\nHead over to the blog to read the full interview and learn about how P&G’s partnership with WWF has been critical for our commitment to nurturing a Nature positive future: https://lnkd.in/gWYn6u8C\n\n#sustainability #nature #WWF #WorldWildlifeDay",
