                "description": "Victoria Jung has dedicated 14 years to innovation at P&G. As Director for the Surface Care Packaging team, Vicki builds packaging innovation plans for Swiffer, Mr. Clean and Microban. \n\nShe enjoys seeing the products she’s worked on hit the shelves and hearing consumers’ reactions. \n  \nAfter launching Mr. Clean Clean Freak, Vicki read a customer review about how easy it is to clean a big surface without having to spray multiple times. “That really made me proud that consumers get the product and package benefits that I’ve worked on,” she said. \n \nHer work on sustainability led her to be recognized as one of Waste 360’s 40 under 40! #ItsOurHome \n\nLearn more about Vicki and how she leads #PGInnovation on our latest blog: https://lnkd.in/ga9muQk2",
