                "description": "In honor of #WomensHistoryMonth here’s a historic look at our Ivorydale Plant soap makers in 1910. We aspire to build a world free from gender bias, with equal voice and representation for all individuals. \n\nWhen everyone sees equal, economies grow, communities are healthier, businesses can thrive, and the world is a better place for everyone.\n\nLearn how we’re creating an inclusive, gender-equal environment within P&G, while advocating for gender and intersectional equality in workplaces everywhere, so that everyone can contribute to their full potential: https://lnkd.in/er-YkJT\n\n#PGHeritage #WeSeeEqual",
