                "date": "4d",
                "description": "For UK LGBTQ+ History Month, Procter & Gamble UK & Ireland has highlighted employees who enrich our workplace culture and increase the value of our brands by being their authentic selves at work every day.\n \nAt P&G, we understand the differences among us engender a greater sense of empathy and understanding that makes us better as a company and helps us grow stronger together as individuals. \n\nCelebrating stories like that of Liam Gordon, Senior IT Manager, Cobalt, is just of the ways we continue to our honor our commitment to driving and sustaining LGBTQ+ visibility, equality, and inclusion, and we look forward to continuing to exercise our leadership and innovation in this space in collaboration with our valued, dedicated employees. \n\nLearn more about how P&G's UK GABLE leaders are driving positive change: https://lnkd.in/gSbCdy8y\n \n#UniqueAndUnited #LGBTQHistoryMonth",
