                "description": "“I enjoy learning and bringing the science behind our brands to life,” says Dr. Atiya Jordan-Brown.  \n \nAtiya works in Scientific Communications for hair care, where she collaborates with dermatologists, marketing leaders, and P&G Beauty scientists to research and communicate the latest hair science technologies externally for Pantene Gold Series, My Black is Beautiful and Head & Shoulders. \n \n“I have experienced challenges throughout my own hair journey as I learned to embrace my coily hair,” she says. “Now I enjoy sharing my love of science and hair with others as a career.” \n \nDiscover more about Atiya and the other #PGInnovation pioneers being highlighted during #BlackHistoryMonth in our latest blog: https://lnkd.in/emhmUpPc",
