                "description": "Does your house have hard water or mineral build up? 85% of American households do. While not harmful, it can lead to residue on your dishes.  \n\nP&G created 9 Elements Foaming Dish Spray to help families combat the effects of hard water. 9 Elements is uniquely formulated to remove unsightly hard water marks while also cutting through grease, coffee and tea stains. \n\nThe spray-activated suds are vinegar-powered with a refreshing lemon scent made from Lemon Essential Oil. And with a reusable sprayer and refill system, 9 Elements Foaming Dish Spray helps reduce plastic waste.  \n\nLearn more about 9 Elements Foaming Dish Spray and the benefits it can have in your home here https://lnkd.in/gyZRFbhj #PGInnovation",
