                "description": "Did you know that something as simple as using your dishwasher instead of handwashing can save you 140 gallons of water a week?\n\nOur Director of Sustainability for North America Home Care, Ashley Fill, dives into all things water conservation in the latest episode of the Sustainability Defined podcast. \n\nLearn how our Home Care team is working toward a water positive future across our manufacturing facilities, our products like Cascade and Dawn that enable people to save water, and our partnerships to help protect biodiversity and restore water in water-stressed areas.\n\nListen here: http://spr.ly/6043OJUGL \n\n#PGHomeCare #SustainabilityDefined #WaterConservation #SustainableBusiness",
