                "description": "Together we are making a meaningful difference with our employees through our brands, with our partners and for communities by: \n\n• Employees who bring their perspectives on how P&G can develop more accessible products like the Ariel ECOCLIC and OLAY’s Easy Open Lid.  \n\n• Premiering two new Queen Collective films presented by OLAY and My Black is Beautiful in partnership with Queen Latifah, Flavor Unit Entertainment and Tribeca on BET. \n\n• Celebrating remarkable women TIME’s 2023 Women of the Year. \n\n• Partnering with Seneca Women and Prosperity Now to launch Secret Deodorant’s Young Women’s Financial Wellness Forum.\n\n• Supporting our LGBTQ+ employees and communities by activating at #SydneyWorldPride.  \n\n#Belonging drives our business. Together we are moving forward. Learn more about belonging at P&G: https://lnkd.in/gVKauYYj",
