                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7049714284771094528",
                "followers": 7408583,
                "date": "5d",
                "description": "For P&G Ventures Product Research Senior Scientist Emma Klingman, consumer and behavioral understanding is at the core of all her work.   \n \n“I love solving difficult problems and finding the sweet spot between delivering a delightful experience for the consumer while growing the brand and category,” Emma says. She does this often as Zevo Products Research Platform Leader at P&G Ventures, which includes insect traps, bug spray and on-body repellents. \n \nEmma put her Consumer and Product Research skills to use working on new Zevo innovations P&G Ventures, driving insights and delivering collaboration during product development cycles that enabled agility in bringing new-to-the-world brands and products to market. \n \n“The way that I communicated with my team had to be incredibly sound to create truly differentiated products in spaces that were ripe for innovation and at a breakneck speed,” she said. “I can’t wait to share our breakthrough innovation with the world.” #PGInnovation \n \nLearn more about P&G Innovations that make spring cleaning easier: http://spr.ly/6041OHQ1v",
