                "urn": "urn:li:activity:7051871787294347264",
                "followers": 7439930,
                "date": "2w",
                "description": "Today, we launched our #ItsOurHome \"Made Better, Made to Save” campaign.   \n\nWhat if sustainable choices did not have to be hard? What if there were simple hacks to live a more sustainable lifestyle, get great results, and – in some cases – even save on household bills? At Procter & Gamble, we are focused on developing innovations that deliver irresistible superiority in a sustainable way. \n\nP&G brands have partnered with digital creators to show just how easy it can be to save water, waste and energy, with products that are made better for our consumers. The creators experienced firsthand how sustainable living can be hard and they used their unique style and humor to engage, entertain and educate their community on how it can be easier with brands that are made to save. #ItsOurHome \n\nLearn how you can make an impact at pggoodeveryday.com.",
