                "description": "New Bounty is more absorbable and durable than previous rolls. P&G’s paper towel scientists say it makes cleaning up messes even better than before. \n\nTune into P&G Live on LinkedIn May 4 at 12PM ET to get all your Bounty questions answered as P&G Reporter Maytal Levi chats with Bounty Senior Scientist Gregg Weaver about this latest #PGInnovation and the technology that went into new Bounty.\n\nLearn more about the technology in new Bounty: https://lnkd.in/gY6-T-2M\n\n#QuickerPickerUpper",
