                "followers": 7439930,
                "date": "1h",
                "description": "At P&G, we’re creating a culture that prioritizes employee wellbeing by building communities of resources and support and destigmatizing the conversation around mental illness. \n\nAfter all, our business can only be at its best when are people are at their best. \n\nA few of our team members are telling their personal stories and sharing how the support they received on their own journeys gave them the strength to recover – and pay it forward to impact a whole new generation of colleagues. \n\nLearn more: https://lnkd.in/gkB5GH3c \n\n#MentalHealthAwarenessMonth",
