                "date": "3d",
                "description": "It’s #ArborDay, and we’re celebrating our #PGHeritage and trees!\n \n#DYK we used to sell fruit trees? 🌳 This old newspaper ad from the 1800s showcased a variety of fruit and ornamental trees, including peach and apple. 🍑 🍎 🍏\n \nToday we’re spotlighting two of our brands, Charmin and EC30, who are teaming up with the Arbor Day Foundation to support #TreePlanting efforts across the United States. \n\nTo learn more about our environmental sustainability commitments, visit https://lnkd.in/ebDnbE9",
