                "description": "Bounty is on a roll with an innovation that’s making the Quicker Picker Upper even better than before. \n\nBehind Bounty is a team of scientists like Senior Scientist Gregg Weaver, who says you have to see it to believe it. \n\n“The new technology in Bounty makes it a triple threat – it’s driven by superior structure, flexible strength and optimized fluid efficiencies,” said Weaver, who has worked on Bounty for more than 20 years.  \n\nTo learn more about Weaver and this latest Bounty innovation: https://lnkd.in/gY6-T-2M\n\n#PGInnovation #QuickerPickerUpper",
